---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy â€” Small Talk Notebook">
  <main class="flex-1 py-16 px-8">
    <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="text-[--color-muted] hover:text-[--color-contrast] transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">
        &larr; Back to home
      </a>

      <h1 class="font-title text-5xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[--color-muted] mb-12">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-[--color-black]">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">The short version</h2>
          <p>Your notes never leave your device. We can't see them. No one can.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">What we collect</h2>
          <p>Nothing. No accounts, no tracking, no analytics. We don't know who you are.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">How your data is stored</h2>
          <p>Everything stays on your device, encrypted. We don't have servers. There's nothing to hack because there's nothing to steal.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">Third-party services</h2>
          <p>None. Zero. We don't use analytics, crash reporting, or any external services.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">Data sharing</h2>
          <p>Never. Your notes never leave your device. We couldn't share them even if we wanted to.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">Your control</h2>
          <p>Delete everything anytime. It's your notebook. Uninstall the app and it's all gone.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-title text-2xl text-[--color-contrast] mb-4">Questions?</h2>
          <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@smalltalknotebook.com" class="text-[--color-highlight] underline">support@smalltalknotebook.com</a></p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-8 px-8 text-center text-sm text-[--color-muted]">
    <nav class="flex justify-center gap-6 mb-4">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[--color-contrast] transition-colors">Home</a>
      <a href="/support" class="hover:text-[--color-contrast] transition-colors">Support</a>
    </nav>
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Small Talk Notebook</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
